    <item>
      <title>当特朗普的关税使市场处于边缘状态时，美国股票消除了损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-stocks-swoon-as-trump-sows-economic-fear-across-wall-street</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票周一疯狂地挥舞着，S＆amp; P 500指数上台上演了令人惊叹的周转，以消除急剧下降的幅度，因为推进了重型股票繁重的股票和投资组合，重新平衡了暂时对唐纳德·特朗普总统周三的关税宣布的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-stocks-swoon-as-trump-sows-economic-fear-across-wall-street</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 13:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
